'''glucosamine'''
#{{biochemistry}} an [[amino]] derivative of [[glucose]] that is a component of [[polysaccharide]]s such as [[chitin]]; it is marketed as a [[dietary supplement]] supposedly to reduce the symptoms of [[arthritis]]

